data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Kissimmee. This spacious and modern beauty is nestled on a conservation lot in a quiet neighborhood. Enjoy unparalleled privacy in your fenced backyard. Inside, the open-concept layout caters to your needs. The first-floor master suite is perfect for multi-generational families. The chef’s kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and stunning quartz countertops. Upstairs, discover three additional spacious bedrooms. The location is unbeatable, near historic downtown Kissimmee and a short drive from Disney World and Universal Studios. Community amenities include pools, tennis courts, and 64 acres of Bald Eagle Preserve. This home is truly move-in ready! ????
